{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"roleHeading":"Case","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot12PropertyHintO5flagsyA2CmF","symbolKind":"case","title":"PropertyHint.flags"},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/PropertyHint"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/propertyhint\/flags"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/PropertyHint\/flags"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hints that an integer property is a bitmask with named bit flags."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"case"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"flags"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The hint string is a comma separated list of names such as ","type":"text"},{"code":"\"Bit0,Bit1,Bit2,Bit3\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". Whitespaces are ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"not","type":"text"}]},{"text":" removed from either end of a name. The first name in the list has value 1, the next 2, then 4, 8, 16 and so on. Explicit values can also be specified by appending ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":":integer"},{"text":" to the name, e.g. ","type":"text"},{"code":"\"A:4,B:8,C:16\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":". You can also combine several flags ("},{"code":"\"A:4,B:8,AB:12,C:16\"","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A flag value must be at least "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"type":"text","text":" and at most "},{"code":"2 ** 32 - 1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note","style":"note"},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Unlike ``PropertyHint\/","type":"text"},{"code":"enum```, the previous explicit value is not taken into account. For the hint ","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"“A:16,B,C”`, A is 16, B is 2, C is 4.","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/PropertyHint":{"fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PropertyHint","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/propertyhint","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","title":"PropertyHint","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/PropertyHint","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PropertyHint","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[],"type":"topic"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/PropertyHint/flags":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"flags","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/propertyhint\/flags","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/PropertyHint\/flags","title":"PropertyHint.flags","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Hints that an integer property is a bitmask with named bit flags."}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Framework to write Godot Game Extensions using the Swift Programming Language."}],"title":"SwiftGodot","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot","role":"collection","type":"topic"}}}